summary: The story will continue to the north, to the frozen continent of Atmora.
descriptionHtml:
New  continent with open towns, story line, daedric quests, guilds quests, miscellaneous quests .etc..  

Pictures with map very soon.

The story of Skyrim and all of Tamriel will continue to the north, to the continent of Atmora, where the conflict betwen races will go to a higher level.
